Package ca.phon.ipa.parser

Enum IPATokenType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<IPATokenType>
      • ca.phon.ipa.parser.IPATokenType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<IPATokenType>
    public enum IPATokenType
extends Enum<IPATokenType>
    Every IPA glyph must have an associated token type. Token types are used during IPAElement parsing and are available via IPATokens.getTokenType(Character)
